      <title>菲律宾即将对 Netflix、HBO 订阅征税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/philippines-moves-closer-to-taxing-netflix-hbo-subscriptions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾立法者批准了一项联合法案，提议对 Netflix、HBO 和 Disney 等外国数字服务征税，旨在确保新的政府收入来源来资助额外支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/philippines-moves-closer-to-taxing-netflix-hbo-subscriptions</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 03:38:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行利用 Metaverse 赢得印度富裕侨民的业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/hsbc-taps-metaverse-to-win-business-from-india-s-rich-diaspora</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰控股有限公司正在测试一系列新产品和服务，以争取从印度富裕侨民手中赢得更多业务份额。去年，印度富裕侨民向国内汇款超过 1000 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-28/hsbc-taps-metaverse-to-win-business-from-india-s-rich-diaspora</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 02:57:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
